 The @{fg highlight}"@{fg text} means a solid bar

 Once you set-up the first 60 framesĀjustĀcopyĀandĀpasteĀtillĀtheĀendĀofĀtheĀanimation.ĀYouĀhave to put 1 frameĀof aĀstateĀandĀthenĀ9ĀframesĀofĀtheĀsameĀstate or the lights willĀfadeĀupĀandĀdown [whichĀisĀwhyĀIĀdidn'tĀuseĀtheĀstrobeĀtexture].
